src:
In mezzo al Viale…
01 Nov 2019, 14:06 by Segnalazione WhatsApp



I Gens cantavano “In fondo al Viale” , evocando struggenti suggestioni sentimentali. Questo scooter, in mezzo al Viale, evoca fastidiose suggestioni di inciviltà.
text:
In the middle of the Avenue ...
01 Nov 2019, 14:06 by WhatsApp Reporting



The Gens sang "At the end of the Avenue", evoking poignant sentimental suggestions. This scooter, in the middle of the Avenue, evokes annoying suggestions of incivility.
